.TH UTILITYKIT 1 "July 2026" "UtilityKit v5.10.6" "UtilityKit Tools"
.SH NAME
utility-release_helper \- Guided pre-release checks for git projects.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B utility release_helper
[\fIoptions\fP]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Guided pre-release checks for git projects.
.SH USAGE
.PP
.EX
bash _release_helper.sh --help
.EE
.PP
.SH CROSS-PLATFORM BEHAVIOR
.PP
All commands are designed to work on Linux, macOS, and Termux/minimal terminals where possible. Optional system dependencies are detected at runtime. If a dependency is unavailable, the tool prints a clear warning and either uses a fallback or skips that feature safely.
.PP
